Detailed Description

cvmx_sriomaint::_erb_pack_capt_2

This register contains bytes 8 through 11 of the packet header. The hardware will not update this register (i.e. this register is locked) while SRIOMAINT()_ERB_ATTR_CAPT[VALID] is set. This register should only be read while this bit is set.
